{"id": 5079, "title": "Ticket #5079: Document shared port daemon problems on Windows", "description": "<blockquote>\nThere are two known problems with the shared port daemon on Windows, and as far as I can see they are not documented:\n<ol>\n<li>The kbdd can't communicate (<span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/tickets?ticket=5058\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('5058'); return false;\" title=\"kbdd does not work with shared port daemon\">#5058</a></span>).\n</li><li>Signals don't work, so the master can't shut things down correctly (<span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"new\" href=\"/tickets?ticket=5078\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('5078'); return false;\" title=\"Signals don't work with shared port daemon on Windows\">#5078</a></span>).</li></ol>\n</blockquote>", "remarks": "<blockquote>\n</blockquote>", "derived_tickets": "", "attachments": "", "check_ins": "", "type": "doc", "last_change": "2015-Jun-03 14:57", "status": "new", "created": "2015-Jun-03 14:55", "fixed_version": "2015-Jun-03 14:55", "broken_version": "v080208", "priority": "3", "subsystem": "DaemonSharedP", "assigned_to": "", "derived_from": "", "creator": "wenger", "rust": "s8549", "customer_group": "other", "visibility": "public", "notify": "wenger@cs.wisc.edu, smoler@cs.wisc.edu", "due_date": ""}